1 AN ACT
2 To enact R.S. 47:463.243, relative to motor vehicle special prestige license plates; to
3 establish the "Krewe of Athena" specialty license plate; to provide for the creation,
4 issuance, design, fees, implementation, distribution, and rule promulgation
5 applicable to such license plate; to provide an effective date; and to provide for
6 related matters.
7 Be it enacted by the Legislature of Louisiana:
8 Section 1. R.S. 47:463.243 is hereby enacted to read as follows:
9 §463.243. Special prestige license plate; "Krewe of Athena"
10 A.(1) The secretary of the Department of Public Safety and Corrections shall
11 establish a special prestige motor vehicle license plate to be known as the "Krewe
12 of Athena" plate, provided there is a minimum of one thousand applicants for such
13 plate. The plate shall be restricted to use on passenger cars, pickup trucks,
14 recreational vehicles, motorcycles, and vans.
15 (2) The Department of Public Safety and Corrections, office of motor
16 vehicles, shall create this special prestige license plate when the applicable statutory
17 provisions are met and the department's electronic vehicle and registration system
18 is updated to accommodate the creation of the new plates.
19 B. The secretary shall work in conjunction with the Krewe of Athena
20 Carnival Club, Inc. to select the color and design of the plate, provided it is in
21 compliance with R.S. 47:463(A)(3). The design shall include the words "Krewe of
22 Athena".
